            Compliance
            




If you wish to report any compliance concerns regarding Biogen or any of its employees or contractors, you may do so in writing at the address provided below or confidentially and anonymously, where permitted by local law, by using the Compliance Helpline. Complaints submitted in this manner will be forwarded directly to the Chair of the Audit Committee.
To submit a report in the U.S and Canada through the Compliance Helpline, call us toll-free at: 1-866-418-2859 (click here for international Compliance Helpline dial-in numbers).
Click here to submit a report online, or write to us at:
Corporate Compliance
Biogen Inc.
225 Binney Street
Cambridge, MA 02142
USA



            Privacy
            




If you have any concerns about the manner in which your personal information has been collected or handled by Biogen, or have any queries in regard to our Privacy Policy, please call us toll-free at: 1-866-418-2859 (click here for international Compliance Helpline dial-in numbers) or email us at privacy@biogen.com.













