OUR COMMITMENT TO SMA

 Working to improve the lives of people with SMA


Learn more



A TRANSFORMATIVE AGE OF NEUROLOGY


As a leading company in the fight against multiple sclerosis, Biogen is applying its expertise to help address some of most challenging and complex diseases of the brain.


Learn More



